<section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
      CarPlatform 이용 방법
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center">
        <%= tabler_icon "search", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">1. 차량 검색</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">원하는 차량 모델, 연식, 가격대 등 다양한 조건으로 차량을 검색합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center">
        <%= tabler_icon "file-invoice", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2. 견적 비교</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">여러 딜러사의 견적과 금융 상품을 한눈에 비교하여 최적의 조건을 선택합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center">
        <%= tabler_icon "car", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">3. 구매 및 출고</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">선택한 차량을 계약하고 안전하게 출고까지 진행합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
